words.example: Please have your boarding pass and passport ready for boarding. (请准备好您的登机牌和护照以便登机。)
You must show your passport at immigration. (你必须在移民局出示你的护照。)
I need to check my large luggage. (我需要托运我的大件行李。)
Our departure is scheduled for 3:15 PM. (我们的出发时间定在下午3点15分。)
The arrival of the flight was delayed by one hour. (航班到达时间延误了一小时。)
After collecting your bags, you will go through customs. (取完行李后，您需要通过海关。)
The flight from London arrives at Terminal 2. (从伦敦来的航班抵达2号航站楼。)
Can you send me your travel itinerary? (你能把你的旅行行程安排发给我吗？)
Our final destination is Bangkok. (我们的最终目的地是曼谷。)
You can do online check-in 24 hours before your flight. (你可以在航班起飞前24小时办理网上值机。)
Please remove your laptop and liquids for security. (请取出您的笔记本电脑和液体物品接受安检。)
Our flight was delayed due to bad weather. (我们的航班因恶劣天气延误了。)
After getting off the plane, follow signs to baggage claim. (下飞机后，请按照指示牌前往行李提取处。)
Do you need a visa to enter that country? (进入那个国家你需要签证吗？)
The train journey offers stunning mountain scenery. (这趟火车旅程提供了令人惊叹的山景。)
